            <title><![CDATA[【#年轻人有高血压应警惕肾脏病#[吃惊]】慢性肾脏病早期三种症状：①水肿。最常表现为晨起上眼睑的浮肿，下午和晚上减轻；②出现类似肥皂水一样绵细不易消散的泡...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E5%BA%94%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E8%82%BE%E8%84%8F%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E5%BA%94%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E8%82%BE%E8%84%8F%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#年轻人有高血压应警惕肾脏病#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】慢性肾脏病早期三种症状：①水肿。最常表现为晨起上眼睑的浮肿，下午和晚上减轻；②出现类似肥皂水一样绵细不易消散的泡沫尿或者尿色发生变化要警惕。如果近期未吃红色火龙果、甜菜根、酚酞含片，但尿色偏红，出现洗肉水样或浓茶色尿，建议到医院就诊检查。③高血压是肾脏病进展的快速因素，年轻患者出现高血压，要警惕肾脏疾病。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%9C%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E8%87%B4%E8%82%BE%E8%84%8F%E5%8F%97%E6%8D%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%9C%AA%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E8%87%B4%E8%82%BE%E8%84%8F%E5%8F%97%E6%8D%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#男子未重视糖尿病致肾脏受损#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6CKsMTf" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
